Package api.equinix.javasdk.networkedge.client

Interface SSHUsers

All Known Implementing Classes:
SSHUsersImpl
public interface SSHUsers
Client interface for managing SSH users on Network Edge devices. Provides operations to list, retrieve, and create SSH users, as well as check username availability.
Version:
$Id: $Id
